original_title: Carmen Electra's Naked Women Wrestling League: Naked Revolution
overview: Carmen Electra presents a series of matches from the NWWL, including Annie Social vs. Trish the Dish, Ninja Chops vs. Kylie Electra, Cleopatra vs. Josianne the Pussycat, April Hunter vs. Melissa Coates and a championship match between reigning champion Kandi Smyth and NWWL newcomer Mandy Weaver.
title: Carmen Electra's Naked Women Wrestling League: Naked Revolution
